- `OnFilesChanged` `EventCallback<List<FileInfo>>` notifies the parent with accepted (non-error) files
- `FileInfo` record defined as `record FileInfo(string Name, long Size, string Type)`

**`Components/FileDropZone.razor.css`** — scoped styles for the drop zone and file list.

**Usage example:**
```razor
<FileDropZone OnFilesChanged="HandleFiles" />

@code {
    private void HandleFiles(List<FileDropZone.FileInfo> files)
    {
        // files contains only accepted (≤10MB) entries
    }
}
```
